{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Step into the battlefield with Warside, a modern iteration on the classic turn-based-tactics formula. Experience an <strong>epic story mode campaign</strong>. Choose between <strong>legendary Commanders</strong>, each with unique playstyles and devastating <strong>Battle Powers</strong>. Master the battlefield with a vast array of terrain and units. All brought to life with <strong>beautiful pixel art</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Choose your Commander, assemble your forces, and battle your way to victory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Over 30 Unit Types</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Storm the battlefield with <strong>tanks</strong> and <strong>artillery</strong>. Master the seas with  <strong>submarines</strong> and  <strong>warships</strong>. Conquer the skies with <strong>helicopters</strong> and <strong>jet aircraft</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368300/extras/Units.gif?t=1736310278\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Command a variety of specialist infantry, including <strong>snipers</strong>, <strong>medics</strong>, <strong>mortar teams</strong>, and <strong>saboteurs</strong>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">14 Playable Commanders</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Choose from 14 Commanders, each with <strong>unique passive skills</strong> and game-changing <strong>Battle Powers</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368300/extras/BattlePowers.gif?t=1736310278\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Battle Powers can be devastating, but they need careful timing to have the most impact. Choose wisely for maximum effect.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Story Campaign</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Test your skills in our epic single-player campaign with <strong>over 30 missions</strong> to master. Classic battles, plus escort, rescue, and covert missions with jaw-dropping story events.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368300/extras/GameScene1.png?t=1736310278\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Battle in beautifully drawn <strong>forest</strong>, <strong>desert</strong>, and <strong>ice</strong> environments, plus the <strong>toxic wastelands</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Multiplayer</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Challenge friends and enemies to thrilling <strong>cross-platform multiplayer</strong> battles. Whether you're side by side or miles apart, the battle is on with both <strong>local</strong> and <strong>online play</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368300/extras/Multiplayer.png?t=1736310278\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Highlights</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Intuitive <strong>turn-based gameplay</strong> with a familiar feel for fans of the classics.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>14 playable Commanders</strong>, each with unique <strong>passive skills</strong> and <strong>Battle Powers</strong>.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Control <strong>30+ unit types</strong>. Simultaneously battle over land, air, and sea with <strong>ground forces</strong>, <strong>aircraft</strong>, and <strong>naval units</strong>.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Faction unique units</strong> with mechanics specific to each faction.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Single-player campaign</strong> with over 30 missions.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Forest</strong>, <strong>desert</strong> and <strong>snow</strong> environments, plus the <strong>toxic wastelands</strong>.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Challenge friends and foes with <strong>multiplayer battles</strong>. Local and internet play are supported.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Design your own maps with the <strong>built-in mission editor</strong> for both single and multiplayer.</p></li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368300/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1736310278","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368300/page.bg.jpg?t=1736310278","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368300/b99da9dc07af49c098cdd624efd419292d49e6b3/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1736310278","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368300/b99da9dc07af49c098cdd624efd419292d49e6b3/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1736310278","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"PvP","id":49},{"description":"Online PvP","id":36},{"description":"LAN PvP","id":47},{"description":"Co-op","id":9},{"description":"Online Co-op","id":38},{"description":"LAN Co-op","id":48},{"description":"Cross-Platform Multiplayer","id":27},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28},{"description":"Includes level editor","id":17},{"description":"Remote Play on TV","id":43}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","demos":[{"appid":3222310,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Step into the battlefield with Warside, a modern iteration on the classic turn-based-tactics formula. Experience an <strong>epic story mode campaign</strong>. C